sons to the previous indices. After the loop, I’ll ensure the permutation is complete by confirming no duplicates or out-of-range values exist, which guarantees all indices are present from 0 to count-1. This function might be helpful for some lookups before searches. I'll need to add a Python reference function and associated tests too."}}
